data.name: xUpperCharLimit.ToolTip
data.value: Determine how many uppercase letters a player can have in their message if the message length is over 10 digits long. If they go over the set amount it sets their whole message to lowercase. Set to 1 for default, which is (rawMessage.Length / 2)
